Are you okay?

33
00:02:26,970 --> 00:02:27,370
Xiao Se.

34
00:02:27,410 --> 00:02:27,900
Xiao Se.

35
00:02:28,060 --> 00:02:28,570
Xiao Se.

36
00:02:29,090 --> 00:02:29,940
Leave.

37
00:02:32,530 --> 00:02:33,300
Qianluo,

38
00:02:33,650 --> 00:02:34,460
we can't just

39
00:02:34,500 --> 00:02:35,370
keep walking like this.

40
00:02:35,780 --> 00:02:36,460
Is there no ally

41
00:02:36,460 --> 00:02:37,130
