43
00:02:38,530 --> 00:02:39,690
I have seldom left Xueyue City

44
00:02:39,690 --> 00:02:40,340
since I was young.

45
00:02:40,650 --> 00:02:41,530
I haven't met many people

46
00:02:41,570 --> 00:02:43,020
in the martial arts world.

47
00:02:43,650 --> 00:02:44,810
I don't know any allies

48
00:02:45,220 --> 00:02:45,940
of Xueyue City.

49
00:02:45,970 --> 00:02:47,250
Let alone looking for one.

50
00:02:47,740 --> 00:02:48,650
What should we do then?

51
00:02:50,410 --> 00:02:50,850
