76
00:03:47,620 --> 00:03:48,410
one step ahead of us.

77
00:03:48,780 --> 00:03:49,410
Is there any ally

78
00:03:49,780 --> 00:03:50,850
of Xueyue City nearby?

79
00:03:53,500 --> 00:03:54,340
Sword Heart Tomb.

80
00:04:00,810 --> 00:04:01,250
Okay.

81
00:04:01,410 --> 00:04:02,250
