87
00:04:12,780 --> 00:04:13,220
He Cong.

88
00:04:14,060 --> 00:04:15,220
What special names.

89
00:04:15,570 --> 00:04:16,450
There's no time for this.

90
00:04:16,940 --> 00:04:17,450
Don't worry.

91
00:04:17,860 --> 00:04:18,660
Divine Healer Hua happens

92
00:04:18,770 --> 00:04:19,860
