93
00:04:19,980 --> 00:04:20,890
I'll take him there.

94
00:04:21,770 --> 00:04:22,180
Come.

95
00:04:24,250 --> 00:04:24,890
Lei,

96
00:04:25,890 --> 00:04:27,370
come to Sword Pavilion with me.

97
00:04:27,860 --> 00:04:29,300
Old Master might want to see you.

98
00:04:29,500 --> 00:04:30,500
Who is Old Master?

99
00:04:31,300 --> 00:04:31,740
You're dumb.

100
00:04:32,320 --> 00:04:33,300
It's certainly the head

101
00:04:33,330 --> 00:04:34,570
