102
00:04:35,300 --> 00:04:36,060
The head?

103
00:04:44,210 --> 00:04:45,540
There are so many swords here.

104
00:04:47,330 --> 00:04:48,420
This is more imposing

105
00:04:48,420 --> 00:04:50,620
than the Sword Chamber in Xueyue City.

106
00:04:53,010 --> 00:04:53,860
By the way, Mingxuan,

107
00:04:54,500 --> 00:04:55,100
why

108
00:04:55,210 --> 00:04:55,980
