109
00:04:57,210 --> 00:04:58,660
I'm here to work on something.

110
00:04:59,810 --> 00:05:01,890
Yet, I saw the Qiancheng Token

111
00:05:02,540 --> 00:05:03,860
explode in the sky

112
00:05:03,890 --> 00:05:04,620
as soon as I got here.

113
00:05:05,980 --> 00:05:08,060
Not many people are eligible

114
00:05:08,100 --> 00:05:08,740
to use it.

115
00:05:08,860 --> 00:05:09,740
So I rushed over.

116
00:05:10,330 --> 00:05:11,300
It turned out to be you.

117
00:05:17,660 --> 00:05:18,010
Lei Wujie.

118
00:05:18,060 --> 00:05:18,810
Come over here.

119
00:05:20,330 --> 00:05:21,620
This is Qilin Fang Sword.

120
00:05:22,540 --> 00:05:23,300
It's the sword

121
00:05:23,330 --> 00:05:24,330
of Qilin's head swordsman, Li Xiuxi.

122
00:05:25,100 --> 00:05:26,300
It ranks 16th on the Records of Famous Swords.

123
00:05:31,300 --> 00:05:32,740
Qilin Fang Sword is a destructive weapon.

124
00:05:33,450 --> 00:05:34,690
If you want to touch it,

125
00:05:35,420 --> 00:05:37,010
[Li Suwang, Sword Heart Tomb]
you might hurt

126
00:05:37,660 --> 00:05:39,060
yourself.

127
00:05:44,420 --> 00:05:44,810
Old Master.

128
00:05:46,370 --> 00:05:47,300
Which one

129
00:05:47,300 --> 00:05:48,940
is the disciple of Fairy Luoxia

130
00:05:49,660 --> 00:05:50,300
who asks to see me?

131
00:05:52,370 --> 00:05:53,210
I'm Luo Mingxuan,

132
00:05:53,570 --> 00:05:54,980
the disciple of Fairy Luoxia.

133
00:05:57,330 --> 00:05:59,540
Is your master doing well?

134
00:06:00,740 --> 00:06:01,210
She's well.

135
00:06:03,690 --> 00:06:06,210
Is she as pretty

136
00:06:06,570 --> 00:06:08,010
as she used to be?

137
00:06:13,660 --> 00:06:14,210
Well,

138
00:06:15,370 --> 00:06:16,330
I've done forging

139
00:06:16,690 --> 00:06:19,010
the swords you requested.

140
00:06:28,660 --> 00:06:31,010
The heavy sword is Desperate,
the light one is Separate,

141
00:06:31,370 --> 00:06:32,540
the long one is Phoenix,

142
00:06:32,940 --> 00:06:34,890
the double swords are Goumang and Calamity,

143
00:06:35,100 --> 00:06:37,100
and the three-foot swords are Wisdom and One-Eye.

144
00:06:37,570 --> 00:06:39,250
There are seven swords in total.

145
00:06:40,210 --> 00:06:42,330
Seven swords? That's generous.

146
00:06:45,180 --> 00:06:45,770
Thank you, Old Master.

147
00:06:46,060 --> 00:06:46,540
You may

148
00:06:47,180 --> 00:06:47,740
have them all.

149
00:06:55,570 --> 00:06:57,010
As for you,

150
00:06:58,010 --> 00:06:58,860
you

151
00:06:59,620 --> 00:07:01,130
look familiar.

152
00:07:07,300 --> 00:07:08,060
Tingyu,

153
00:07:08,860 --> 00:07:10,980
it's been a long time.

154
00:07:11,570 --> 00:07:13,450
You know this sword, sir?

155
00:07:14,300 --> 00:07:16,500
Tingyu, Guanxue, Wanghua, and Wenfeng.

156
00:07:16,860 --> 00:07:17,810
I forged

157
00:07:18,370 --> 00:07:20,300
the Elegant Four Swords when I was young.

158
00:07:20,570 --> 00:07:22,100
I certainly recognize it.

159
00:07:31,250 --> 00:07:34,100
You forged the Elegant Four Swords?

160
00:07:36,180 --> 00:07:37,330
Are you

161
00:07:38,180 --> 00:07:38,860
Li Suwang?

162
00:07:40,660 --> 00:07:41,450
Wait a minute?

163
00:07:42,100 --> 00:07:44,130
Weren't you already dead?

164
00:07:44,620 --> 00:07:45,010
You...

165
00:07:46,100 --> 00:07:47,370
Nonsense.

166
00:07:47,860 --> 00:07:49,500
I just haven't shown up in the martial arts world

167
00:07:49,570 --> 00:07:51,100
for a couple of dozen years.

168
00:07:51,570 --> 00:07:52,540
Who told you I was dead?

169
00:07:53,420 --> 00:07:54,940
But rumor has it,

170
00:07:55,500 --> 00:07:56,620
the master of Sword Heart Tomb

171
00:07:56,690 --> 00:07:57,940
is your brother,

172
00:07:58,010 --> 00:07:58,740
Li Suchen.

173
00:07:59,570 --> 00:08:00,370
The rumor

174
00:08:00,420 --> 00:08:01,180
is not trustworthy.

175
00:08:05,940 --> 00:08:06,420
Grandfather?

176
00:08:12,210 --> 00:08:13,250
I'm such an unfilial grandson,

177
00:08:13,940 --> 00:08:14,570
Grandfather.

178
00:08:19,860 --> 00:08:21,420
Get up, get up.

179
00:08:26,010 --> 00:08:27,010
You're good at swordsmanship.

180
00:08:27,540 --> 00:08:28,540
Then you're not unfilial at all.

181
00:08:30,100 --> 00:08:32,020
Since you got Tingyu Sword,

182
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:34,850
you must've met your sister.

183
00:08:37,260 --> 00:08:37,850
Good.

184
00:08:40,820 --> 00:08:41,650
Your sister

185
00:08:42,130 --> 00:08:43,650
is the unfilial one.

186
00:08:44,300 --> 00:08:46,460
She knew I was

187
00:08:46,580 --> 00:08:47,890
at Sword Heart Tomb

188
00:08:47,980 --> 00:08:48,650
all alone,

189
00:08:48,730 --> 00:08:49,940
but she didn't come and see me.

190
00:08:50,460 --> 00:08:52,130
It's not like

191
00:08:52,340 --> 00:08:53,250
I'd force her

192
00:08:53,460 --> 00:08:54,220
to be the master

193
00:08:54,250 --> 00:08:55,460
of Sword Heart Tomb.

194
00:08:55,770 --> 00:08:57,180
Why is she afraid of me?

195
00:08:57,850 --> 00:08:58,650
Tingyu Sword

196
00:08:58,940 --> 00:09:00,460
is a punishment for her.

197
00:09:01,180 --> 00:09:01,980
I confiscate it.

198
00:09:03,530 --> 00:09:03,980
But...

199
00:09:05,890 --> 00:09:06,940
Don't worry.

200
00:09:07,490 --> 00:09:09,460
Come to the Sword Pavilion tonight.

201
00:09:10,180 --> 00:09:11,420
I'll give you

202
00:09:12,010 --> 00:09:13,300
a more powerful sword.

203
00:09:27,980 --> 00:09:29,220
There's no wound.

204
00:09:29,940 --> 00:09:31,460
But he's got an irregular pulse.

205
00:09:32,340 --> 00:09:33,370
It's really rare.

206
00:09:33,370 --> 00:09:34,680
[Hua Jin, Medicine Valley]

207
00:10:02,890 --> 00:10:03,340
Let's go.

208
00:10:05,490 --> 00:10:06,770
Miss Ye, are you okay?

209
00:10:07,820 --> 00:10:08,340
I'm fine.

210
00:10:09,180 --> 00:10:10,250
I'm just a bit tired.

211
00:10:13,100 --> 00:10:14,340
Why is your pulse so irregular?

212
00:10:15,980 --> 00:10:16,650
They're coming.

213
00:10:17,060 --> 00:10:17,650
Keep on moving.

214
00:10:18,100 --> 00:10:18,530
Okay.

215
00:10:20,530 --> 00:10:21,530
We're already here.

216
00:10:22,770 --> 00:10:23,460
Martial Uncle?

217
00:10:23,820 --> 00:10:24,490
Go back with me.

218
00:10:27,850 --> 00:10:28,850
Are you going to betray the clan?

219
00:10:30,130 --> 00:10:31,340
But I'm with two clans.

220
00:10:31,580 --> 00:10:32,700
But your surname is Tang.

221
00:10:33,340 --> 00:10:34,370
Why must you do this?

222
00:10:34,610 --> 00:10:35,530
Does Tang Clan really

223
00:10:35,530 --> 00:10:36,770
have to do such a treacherous thing?

224
00:10:36,850 --> 00:10:38,490
This is not your concern.

225
00:10:39,130 --> 00:10:40,180
As a disciple of Tang Clan,

226
00:10:40,530 --> 00:10:42,010
all you need to do is obey orders.

227
00:10:43,420 --> 00:10:44,530
But Master Baili told me

228
00:10:45,060 --> 00:10:46,130
we got to do things in all conscience.

229
00:10:46,180 --> 00:10:47,060
That's enough, Tang Lian.

230
00:10:47,460 --> 00:10:49,420
Don't you forget your surname, Tang.

231
00:10:50,980 --> 00:10:51,580
Back then,

232
00:10:52,340 --> 00:10:54,060
it was you who sent him to Xueyue City.

233
00:10:54,420 --> 00:10:55,250
Now you want to cut ties

234
00:10:55,300 --> 00:10:56,530
between him and Xueyue City.

235
00:10:57,460 --> 00:10:59,220
Tang Clan is a century-old great family.

236
00:10:59,650 --> 00:11:00,490
Is this how the clan treats

237
00:11:00,490 --> 00:11:01,420
their disciples?

238
00:11:02,220 --> 00:11:02,730
Tang Lian,

239
00:11:03,370 --> 00:11:05,010
I'll give you one last chance.

240
00:11:06,100 --> 00:11:07,300
You're the best disciple

241
00:11:07,370 --> 00:11:08,580
of Tang Clan among your peers.

242
00:11:09,340 --> 00:11:10,340
I hope you won't make

243
00:11:10,340 --> 00:11:11,490
the wrong choice.

244
00:11:12,460 --> 00:11:13,010
Tang Lian.

245
00:11:13,730 --> 00:11:14,420
Miss Ye,

246
00:11:15,060 --> 00:11:15,730
leave.

247
00:11:16,610 --> 00:11:17,530
Find the nearest troop.

248
00:11:18,180 --> 00:11:18,650
Go!

249
00:11:32,850 --> 00:11:33,850
Watch out, Miss Ye!

250
00:11:39,180 --> 00:11:40,340
It's been so long since I used this.

251
00:11:40,980 --> 00:11:42,300
I almost forgot its name.

252
00:11:43,610 --> 00:11:45,100
Mind Peace Bell Technique.

253
00:11:45,610 --> 00:11:47,730
Yes, that's the name.

254
00:11:48,100 --> 00:11:48,580
Wu...

255
00:11:49,490 --> 00:11:50,060
Ye Anshi.

256
00:11:50,700 --> 00:11:52,010
I was Ye Anshi at Tianwaitian.

257
00:11:52,490 --> 00:11:53,490
Now that I've returned to Central Plains.

258
00:11:53,850 --> 00:11:54,820
It's better to call me Wuxin.

259
00:11:55,580 --> 00:11:56,250
Thanks for your help.

260
00:11:56,370 --> 00:11:57,250
Oh, it's you.

261
00:11:57,730 --> 00:11:59,300
I let you go back to Tianwaitian last time.

262
00:11:59,700 --> 00:12:00,370
How dare you

263
00:12:00,370 --> 00:12:01,420
return to Central Plains?

264
00:12:03,300 --> 00:12:03,980
Let me go back?

265
00:12:04,370 --> 00:12:05,130
You?

266
00:12:11,730 --> 00:12:12,100
Let's go.

267
00:12:16,250 --> 00:12:17,250
Have you stopped Jingxia?

268
00:12:19,850 --> 00:12:20,820
I got the information today

269
00:12:21,530 --> 00:12:23,010
that Su Muyu, the head of Su family from Dark River,

270
00:12:23,220 --> 00:12:24,490
and Xie Qidao, the head of Xie family,

271
00:12:24,820 --> 00:12:26,420
joined forces to stop Li Hanyi
from heading North.

272
00:12:26,850 --> 00:12:28,180
But Li Hanyi saw through the ambush

273
00:12:28,610 --> 00:12:29,650
and eventually broke through.

274
00:12:29,940 --> 00:12:30,890
Her whereabouts are still unknown.

275
00:12:31,340 --> 00:12:32,010
It seems like

276
00:12:32,940 --> 00:12:34,340
Dark River is making a move.

277
00:12:34,940 --> 00:12:36,530
Jingxia is too assertive.

278
00:12:37,460 --> 00:12:38,300
What about the three old masters of Tang Clan?

279
00:12:39,060 --> 00:12:39,940
They didn't want

280
00:12:40,180 --> 00:12:41,100
to come forward.

281
00:12:41,650 --> 00:12:42,530
But Li Hanyi already

282
00:12:42,580 --> 00:12:43,530
broke through that time.

283
00:12:44,420 --> 00:12:45,650
They got no choice but to come out.

284
00:12:46,180 --> 00:12:47,060
They still failed to get her.

285
00:12:49,010 --> 00:12:49,730
As for the reason

286
00:12:49,770 --> 00:12:51,220
why Tang Clan would work with Dark River,

287
00:12:52,700 --> 00:12:53,580
I guess it's because

